---
import Base from "../../layouts/Base.astro";

const title = "Lingoda Review 2026: Is the Lingoda Sprint Worth It?";
const description = "Lingoda offers structured group and private classes with native teachers. We look at their unique 'Sprint' challenge and see if it is the best way to master English fast.";
---

<Base title={title} description={description}>
<article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
  <div class="mb-8">
    <span class="text-sm text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Review · Updated April 2026</span>
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold mt-1 mb-4 text-white leading-tight">Lingoda Review 2026: Is the Lingoda Sprint Worth It?</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-400 leading-relaxed">Lingoda offers structured group and private classes with native teachers. We look at their unique "Sprint" challenge and see if it is the best way to master English fast.</p>
  </div>

  <!-- Verdict Box -->
  <div class="bg-emerald-950/20 border-2 border-emerald-500/30 rounded-2xl p-8 mb-12 shadow-sm">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:grid md:grid-cols-3 md:items-center gap-6">
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-emerald-400 text-lg mb-1 italic">Our Verdict</p>
        <p class="text-4xl font-black text-emerald-500">8.7/10</p>
      </div>
      <div class="border-l-0 md:border-l-2 border-emerald-500/20 md:pl-8">
        <p class="text-sm text-emerald-500 font-bold uppercase tracking-tighter">Best for</p>
        <p class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Serious learners who want a structured, school-like environment and a challenge.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center md:text-right">
        <a href="https://learnenglish.life/go/lingoda" class="inline-block bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-700 text-white font-bold py-4 px-8 rounded-xl transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-emerald-900/50 text-center">
          Join the Sprint
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="text-sm text-neutral-500 mb-8 italic">Affiliate Disclosure: LearnEnglish.Life is supported by its readers. When you buy through links on our site, we may earn an affiliate commission at no extra cost to you.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">What is Lingoda?</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Lingoda is a leading online language school based in Germany. Unlike marketplaces that just connect you with tutors, Lingoda provides a complete curriculum. They offer classes for English, Business English, German, French, and Spanish. All classes are led by native speakers and take place in a small group setting or 1-on-1.</p>
  
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">The platform is designed to mimic a real physical school. You follow a specific path from level A1 to C1. After you finish a level, you receive a certificate that follows the Common European Framework of Reference for Languages (CEFR). This makes Lingoda a popular choice for students who need to prove their language level for work or university.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white text-center">Lingoda Features</h2>
  <div class="overflow-x-auto my-8">
    <table class="w-full text-left border-collapse bg-neutral-900 rounded-xl shadow-sm overflow-hidden border border-neutral-800">
      <thead>
        <tr class="bg-neutral-800 border-b border-neutral-700">
          <th class="p-4 font-bold text-white">Feature</th>
          <th class="p-4 font-bold text-white">Details</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody class="text-neutral-300">
        <tr class="border-b border-neutral-800">
          <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-white">Native Teachers</td>
          <td class="p-4">All classes are taught by qualified, native-level speakers.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-neutral-800">
          <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-white">Small Group Classes</td>
          <td class="p-4">Usually 3 to 5 students per class for maximum participation.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-neutral-800">
          <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-white">CEFR Certificates</td>
          <td class="p-4">Earn official certificates as you complete each language level.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="border-b border-neutral-800">
          <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-white">Lingoda Sprint</td>
          <td class="p-4">A high-intensity challenge with a chance to get 50% or 100% cashback.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td class="p-4 font-semibold text-white">24/7 Availability</td>
          <td class="p-4">Book classes at any time of the day or night.</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">The Lingoda Sprint: How It Works</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">The Sprint is Lingoda's most famous feature. It is a two-month challenge designed to push your English to the next level. There are two versions: the Sprint and the Super Sprint. In the regular Sprint, you take 15 classes per month. In the Super Sprint, you take 30 classes per month (one class every single day).</p>

  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">The most exciting part of the Sprint is the reward. If you attend every single class and follow the strict rules, Lingoda will give you 50% cashback for the Sprint or 100% cashback for the Super Sprint. This means you could potentially learn English for free. However, the rules are very strict. You cannot be late, and you cannot miss a single class for any reason. It is a high-risk, high-reward way to learn.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Teaching Method and Curriculum</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Lingoda uses a communicative approach. Each lesson is 60 minutes long and focuses on a specific topic or skill. Before the class, you can download the lesson materials (PDFs) to prepare. During the class, the teacher guides you through exercises, encourages conversation, and corrects your mistakes.</p>

  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">The curriculum is very well-organized. It covers grammar, vocabulary, reading, and speaking. Because you often have different teachers for different classes, you get used to hearing various accents and teaching styles. This is great for real-world listening skills. The small group size ensures that you get enough "talk time" to practice what you are learning.</p>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Lingoda Pricing</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Lingoda offers monthly subscriptions based on the number of classes you want to take. Prices vary depending on whether you choose group or private lessons.</p>
  <ul class="list-none space-y-4 mb-8">
    <li class="flex items-start bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800">
      <span class="text-emerald-500 mr-3 font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-white">Maintainer (4 classes / month)</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400">Starting around $60 per month. Good for keeping your skills fresh.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800">
      <span class="text-emerald-500 mr-3 font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-white">High Flyer (12 classes / month)</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400">Starting around $160 per month. Best for steady progress.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start bg-neutral-900 p-4 rounded-lg border border-neutral-800">
      <span class="text-emerald-500 mr-3 font-bold text-xl">✓</span>
      <div>
        <p class="font-bold text-white">Marathon (Long-term plans)</p>
        <p class="text-neutral-400">Lower price per class if you commit to 3, 6, or 12 months.</p>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Pros and Cons</h2>
  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-emerald-950/20 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-emerald-500/20">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-emerald-400 mb-4">What we love</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-300">
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-emerald-500 mr-2 text-xl">●</span> Professional, native-speaking teachers.</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-emerald-500 mr-2 text-xl">●</span> Structured curriculum with CEFR certificates.</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-emerald-500 mr-2 text-xl">●</span> The Sprint challenge is incredibly motivating.</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-emerald-500 mr-2 text-xl">●</span> Flexible scheduling 24/7.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-red-950/20 p-6 rounded-2xl border border-red-500/20">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-red-400 mb-4">What could be better</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-300">
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-red-500 mr-2 text-xl">●</span> Sprint rules are very strict and easy to fail.</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-red-500 mr-2 text-xl">●</span> Group classes can sometimes feel slow if other students are not prepared.</li>
        <li class="flex items-center"><span class="text-red-500 mr-2 text-xl">●</span> Private lessons are quite expensive compared to marketplaces.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mt-12 mb-6 text-white">Verdict: Is Lingoda Worth it?</h2>
  <p class="text-neutral-300 mb-6 leading-relaxed text-lg">Lingoda is one of the most reliable online language schools available today. If you need structure, a proven curriculum, and official certificates, it is an excellent investment. The Sprint challenge is a unique opportunity to make massive progress in a short time, potentially for free. However, if you prefer casual conversation or a very low price, you might be better off with a platform like iTalki. For serious learners, Lingoda is hard to beat.</p>

  <div class="mt-12 bg-neutral-900 rounded-3xl p-10 text-center text-white shadow-2xl border border-neutral-800">
    <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Ready to master English?</h3>
    <p class="text-neutral-400 mb-8 text-lg max-w-xl mx-auto">Start your 7-day free trial today or join the next Lingoda Sprint to challenge yourself and earn your cashback.</p>
    <a href="https://learnenglish.life/go/lingoda" class="inline-block bg-emerald-500 hover:bg-emerald-400 text-neutral-950 font-black py-5 px-12 rounded-2xl transition-all transform hover:scale-105 text-xl">
      Try Lingoda Now
    </a>
    <p class="mt-6 text-xs text-neutral-500 uppercase tracking-widest font-semibold">Affiliate Disclosure: We may earn a commission if you sign up through our link.</p>
  </div>
</article>
</Base>
